00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.859
hi today

00:00:00.860 --> 00:00:02.832
I will explain the European union

00:00:02.867 --> 00:00:03.767
and its operation

00:00:03.768 --> 00:00:05.239
the European Union is a union

00:00:05.240 --> 00:00:06.779
political and economic

00:00:06.780 --> 00:00:08.239
composed of 27 states

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:09.372
I put you a card

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:11.063
of all the countries that are present

00:00:11.064 --> 00:00:14.119
the first countries are western germany italy

00:00:14.120 --> 00:00:15.531
france the Netherlands

00:00:15.532 --> 00:00:17.183
belgium and luxembourg

00:00:17.184 --> 00:00:18.705
the continent should not be confused

00:00:18.959 --> 00:00:20.989
with the European Union

00:00:20.990 --> 00:00:23.280
there is also the schengen space

00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:25.137
free movement space

00:00:25.138 --> 00:00:26.912
which means that there is no need for a passport

00:00:26.913 --> 00:00:29.087
there is also the euro zone

00:00:29.088 --> 00:00:31.470
all the countries have adopted the currency

00:00:31.473 --> 00:00:33.232
how the eu works

00:00:33.233 --> 00:00:34.819
there are four important places

00:00:34.820 --> 00:00:36.572
the european council in brussels

00:00:36.573 --> 00:00:38.930
the 27 Heads of State and Government

00:00:39.073 --> 00:00:40.453
sit to impulse

00:00:40.573 --> 00:00:42.755
orientations for the European Union

00:00:42.756 --> 00:00:44.995
the European Commission is also

00:00:44.996 --> 00:00:47.847
in brussels the chief and ursula von der leyen

00:00:47.848 --> 00:00:50.259
there are 27 commissioners who propose laws

00:00:50.260 --> 00:00:53.211
the eu council is also located in brussels

00:00:53.304 --> 00:00:55.799
there are 27 ministers who sit there

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:57.746
and there is the European Parliament

00:00:57.873 --> 00:00:58.838
in strasbourg

00:00:58.839 --> 00:01:01.959
where the seven hundred and five MEPs are elected

00:01:01.960 --> 00:01:02.784
these two bodies

00:01:02.973 --> 00:01:05.679
vote on European budgets and laws

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:07.979
there is also the European Central Bank

00:01:07.980 --> 00:01:09.298
located in francfort

00:01:09.299 --> 00:01:11.358
this organization is supranational

00:01:11.359 --> 00:01:11.815
that is, 

00:01:11.815 --> 00:01:13.288
these laws are more important

